Chitkul, nestled in the Baspa Valley, is a paradise for nature lovers and adventure seekers. Surrounded by snow-capped peaks and the serene Baspa River, this untouched village offers stunning landscapes, traditional Himachali wooden houses, and some of the most peaceful trekking trails in Himachal. Whether you seek adventure, spirituality, or just a quiet escape, Chitkul promises an unforgettable experience. Plan your visit with **Pahari Yatri** and explore this hidden gem!
